      Default Constructor for Appointment
      Parameters:
      Appointment_ID - Unique integer value associated to the appointment
      Title - String value indicating the name of the appointment
      Description - String describing the appointment in more detail
      Location - String that shows the location where the appointment is set
      Type - String category for the appointment
      Start - LocalDateTime object providing the start time and date of the meeting
      End - LocalDateTime object providing the end time and date of the meeting
      Customer_ID - integer customer id
      User_ID - integer user id
      Contact_ID - integer contact id
